168 struct npc_manaforge_spawnAI : public ScriptedAI
169 {
170  npc_manaforge_spawnAI(Creature* pCreature) : ScriptedAI(pCreature) { Reset(); }
171 
172  ObjectGuid m_manaforgeGuid;
173 
174  void Reset() override
175  {
176  m_creature->ClearInCombat();
177  }
178 
179  void EnterEvadeMode() override
180  {
181  Reset();
182  Creature *manaforge;
183 
184  if (m_manaforgeGuid)
185  {
186  manaforge = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(m_manaforgeGuid);
187  if (manaforge)
188  {
189  uint32 uiManaforgeEntry = manaforge->GetEntry();
190 
191  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->Clear();
192  float fDistance = m_creature->GetDistance(manaforge);
193  if (fDistance < 20) // If within cast range
194  {
195  m_creature->SetFacingToObject(manaforge);
196  if (uiManaforgeEntry == NPC_ARA_C_CONSOLE)
197  {
198  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(0, m_creature->GetPositionX(), m_creature->GetPositionY(), m_creature->GetPositionZ()); // Why must I do this? They walk back to spawn point otherwise (and only ara mobs do this)
199  m_creature->CastSpell(m_creature, SPELL_INTERRUPT_2, TRIGGERED_OLD_TRIGGERED); // Ara mobs
200 
201  }
202  else
203  m_creature->CastSpell(m_creature, SPELL_INTERRUPT_1, TRIGGERED_OLD_TRIGGERED); // Other consoles
204 
205  }
206  else
207  {
208  // Otherwise need to move closer
209  float fX, fY; // fZ will just be creatures own z
210  float fAngle = m_creature->GetAngle(manaforge);
211  uint32 uiMPID; // need to set this accoringly so creature will cast spell after running
212 
213  switch (uiManaforgeEntry)
214  {
215  case NPC_DURO_C_CONSOLE:
216  uiMPID = 1;
217  break;
218  case NPC_BNAAR_C_CONSOLE:
219  uiMPID = 3;
220  break;
221  default:
222  uiMPID = 0;
223  break;
224  }
225 
226  /* Given an origin (x,y) and line distance "d" which makes an angle "a" with the x-axis, the coordinates for the other point are:
227  * x' = x + (d * cos(a))
228  * y' = y + (d * sin(a)) */
229 
230  fX = m_creature->GetPositionX() + ((fDistance - 15) * cosf(fAngle));
231  fY = m_creature->GetPositionY() + ((fDistance - 15) * sinf(fAngle));
232 
233  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(uiMPID, fX, fY, m_creature->GetPositionZ());
234  }
235  }
236  }
237  }
238 
239  void UpdateAI(const uint32 /*uiDiff*/) override
240  {
241  if (!m_creature->SelectHostileTarget() || !m_creature->GetVictim())
242  return;
243 
244  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
245  }
246 };
247 
248 UnitAI* GetAI_npc_manaforge_spawnAI(Creature* pCreature)
249 {
250  return new npc_manaforge_spawnAI(pCreature);
251 }

279  void ResetControlConsoleAndDespawn()
280  {
281  for (ObjectGuid& guid : m_vSummonGuids)
282  {
283  if (Creature* summon = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(guid))
284  summon->ForcedDespawn(100); // requires delay, to prevent calling spell::cancel, as the call can originate from channeled spell finish
285  }
286  m_vSummonGuids.clear();
287 
288  switch (m_creature->GetEntry())
289  {
290  case NPC_BNAAR_C_CONSOLE:
291  if (GameObject* pGo = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(m_creature, GO_BANAAR_C_CONSOLE, 20.0f))
292  pGo->RemoveFlag(GAMEOBJECT_FLAGS, GO_FLAG_IN_USE);
293  break;
294  case NPC_CORUU_C_CONSOLE:
295  if (GameObject* pGo = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(m_creature, GO_CORUU_C_CONSOLE, 20.0f))
296  pGo->RemoveFlag(GAMEOBJECT_FLAGS, GO_FLAG_IN_USE);
297  break;
298  case NPC_DURO_C_CONSOLE:
299  if (GameObject* pGo = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(m_creature, GO_DURO_C_CONSOLE, 20.0f))
300  pGo->RemoveFlag(GAMEOBJECT_FLAGS, GO_FLAG_IN_USE);
301  break;
302  case NPC_ARA_C_CONSOLE:
303  if (GameObject* pGo = GetClosestGameObjectWithEntry(m_creature, GO_ARA_C_CONSOLE, 20.0f))
304  pGo->RemoveFlag(GAMEOBJECT_FLAGS, GO_FLAG_IN_USE);
305  break;
306  }
307  m_creature->ForcedDespawn();
308  }

310  void DoFailEvent()
311  {
312  DoScriptText(EMOTE_ABORT, m_creature);
313 
314  // Fail players quests
315  // Handle all players in group (if they took quest)
316 
317  if (Player* pPlayer = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid))
318  {
319  if (Group* pGroup = pPlayer->GetGroup())
320  {
321  for (GroupReference* pRef = pGroup->GetFirstMember(); pRef != nullptr; pRef = pRef->next())
322  {
323  if (Player* pMember = pRef->getSource())
324  {
325  switch (m_creature->GetEntry())
326  {
327  case NPC_BNAAR_C_CONSOLE:
328  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
329  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_ALDOR);
330  else if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
331  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_SCRYERS);
332  break;
333  case NPC_CORUU_C_CONSOLE:
334  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
335  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_ALDOR);
336  else if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
337  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_SCRYERS);
338  break;
339  case NPC_DURO_C_CONSOLE:
340  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
341  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_ALDOR);
342  else if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
343  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_SCRYERS);
344  break;
345  case NPC_ARA_C_CONSOLE:
346  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
347  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_ALDOR);
348  else if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
349  pMember->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_SCRYERS);
350  break;
351  }
352  }
353  }
354  }
355  else
356  {
357  switch (m_creature->GetEntry())
358  {
359  case NPC_BNAAR_C_CONSOLE:
360  if (pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
361  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_ALDOR);
362  else
363  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_SCRYERS);
364  break;
365  case NPC_CORUU_C_CONSOLE:
366  if (pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
367  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_ALDOR);
368  else
369  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_SCRYERS);
370  break;
371  case NPC_DURO_C_CONSOLE:
372  if (pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
373  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_ALDOR);
374  else
375  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_SCRYERS);
376  break;
377  case NPC_ARA_C_CONSOLE:
378  if (pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
379  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_ALDOR);
380  else
381  pPlayer->FailQuest(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_SCRYERS);
382  break;
383  }
384  }
385  }

675  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override
676  {
677  if (m_uiHardResetTimer <= uiDiff)
678  {
679  m_uiWaveTimer = 0;
680  m_uiPhase = 1;
681  m_bWave = false;
682  m_bShutdownSaid = false;
683  // why are we here? event should have failed or completed by now...
684  sLog.outCustomLog("Manaforge invalid state, helper creature: %s (%u)", m_creature->GetName(), m_creature->GetEntry());
685  sLog.outCustomLog("uiWaveTimer: %u", m_uiWaveTimer);
686  sLog.outCustomLog("uiPhase: %u", m_uiPhase);
687  sLog.outCustomLog("bWave: %s", (m_bWave ? "true" : "false"));
688  ResetControlConsoleAndDespawn();
689  }
690  else
691  m_uiHardResetTimer -= uiDiff;
692 
693  if (m_uiEventTimer < uiDiff)
694  {
695  Player* pPlayer = m_creature->GetMap()->GetPlayer(m_playerGuid);
696 
697  if (!pPlayer)
698  {
699  ResetControlConsoleAndDespawn();
700  return;
701  }
702 
703  switch (m_uiPhase)
704  {
705  case 1:
706  DoScriptText(EMOTE_START, m_creature, pPlayer);
707  m_uiEventTimer = 60000;
708  m_bWave = true;
709  ++m_uiPhase;
710  break;
711  case 2:
712  DoScriptText(EMOTE_60, m_creature, pPlayer);
713  m_uiEventTimer = 30000;
714  ++m_uiPhase;
715  break;
716  case 3:
717  DoScriptText(EMOTE_30, m_creature, pPlayer);
718  m_uiEventTimer = 20000;
719  DoFinalSpawnForCreature(m_creature);
720  ++m_uiPhase;
721  break;
722  case 4:
723  DoScriptText(EMOTE_10, m_creature, pPlayer);
724  m_uiEventTimer = 10000;
725  m_bWave = false;
726  ++m_uiPhase;
727  break;
728  case 5:
729  DoScriptText(EMOTE_COMPLETE, m_creature, pPlayer);
730  DoCastSpellIfCan(m_creature, SPELL_DISABLE_VISUAL);
731 
732  // Give credit for completion
733  // Handle all players in group (if they took quest)
734  if (Group* pGroup = pPlayer->GetGroup())
735  {
736  for (GroupReference* pRef = pGroup->GetFirstMember(); pRef != nullptr; pRef = pRef->next())
737  {
738  if (Player* pMember = pRef->getSource())
739  {
740  switch (m_creature->GetEntry())
741  {
742  case NPC_BNAAR_C_CONSOLE:
743  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE
744  || pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_BNAAR_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
745  pMember->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
746  break;
747  case NPC_CORUU_C_CONSOLE:
748  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE
749  || pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
750  pMember->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
751  break;
752  case NPC_DURO_C_CONSOLE:
753  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE
754  || pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
755  pMember->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
756  break;
757  case NPC_ARA_C_CONSOLE:
758  if (pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE
759  || pMember->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
760  pMember->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
761  break;
762  }
763  }
764  }
765  }
766  else
767  {
768  switch (m_creature->GetEntry())
769  {
770  case NPC_BNAAR_C_CONSOLE:
771  pPlayer->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
772  break;
773  case NPC_CORUU_C_CONSOLE:
774  if (pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE
775  || pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_CORUU_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
776  pPlayer->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
777  break;
778  case NPC_DURO_C_CONSOLE:
779  if (pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE
780  || pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_DURO_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
781  pPlayer->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
782  break;
783  case NPC_ARA_C_CONSOLE:
784  if (pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_ALDOR) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE
785  || pPlayer->GetQuestStatus(QUEST_SHUTDOWN_ARA_SCRYERS) == QUEST_STATUS_INCOMPLETE)
786  pPlayer->KilledMonsterCredit(m_creature->GetEntry(), m_creature->GetObjectGuid());
787  break;
788  }
789  }
790 
791  ResetControlConsoleAndDespawn();
792  break;
793  }
794  }
795  else
796  m_uiEventTimer -= uiDiff;
797 
798  if (m_bWave)
799  {
800  if (m_uiWaveTimer < uiDiff)
801  {
802  DoWaveSpawnForCreature(m_creature);
803  }
804  else
805  m_uiWaveTimer -= uiDiff;
806  }
807  }
808 };

1084  void UpdateAI(const uint32 uiDiff) override

1088  return;
1089 
1090  // Phase timing
1091  if (m_uiPhaseTimer >= uiDiff)
1092  {
1093  m_uiPhaseTimer -= uiDiff;
1094  return;

1096

1098  Creature* pPathaleon = m_creature->GetMap()->GetCreature(m_pathaleonGuid);

1100 
1101  if (!pArdonis || !pPlayer)
1102  {
1103  Reset();
1104  return;
1105  }
1106 
1107  if (m_uiPhase > 4 && !pPathaleon)
1108  {
1109  Reset();
1110  return;
1111  }
1112 
1113  switch (m_uiPhase)
1114  {
1115  case 1:
1116  DoScriptText(SAY_COMMANDER_DAWNFORGE_1, m_creature);
1117  ++m_uiPhase;
1118  m_uiPhaseTimer = 16000;
1119  break;
1120  case 2:
1121  DoScriptText(SAY_ARCANIST_ARDONIS_1, pArdonis);
1122  ++m_uiPhase;
1123  m_uiPhaseTimer = 16000;
1124  break;
1125  case 3:
1126  DoScriptText(SAY_COMMANDER_DAWNFORGE_2, m_creature);
1127  ++m_uiPhase;
1128  m_uiPhaseTimer = 16000;
1129  break;
1130  case 4:
1131  // spawn pathaleon's image
1132  m_creature->SummonCreature(NPC_PATHALEON_THE_CALCULATOR_IMAGE, 2325.851563f, 2799.534668f, 133.084229f, 6.038996f, TEMPSPAWN_TIMED_DESPAWN, 90000);
1133  ++m_uiPhase;
1134  m_uiPhaseTimer = 500;
1135  break;
1136  case 5:
1137  DoScriptText(SAY_PATHALEON_THE_CALCULATOR_IMAGE_1, pPathaleon);
1138  ++m_uiPhase;
1139  m_uiPhaseTimer = 6000;
1140  break;
1141  case 6:
1142  switch (m_uiPhaseSubphase)
1143  {
1144  case 0:
1145  TurnToPathaleonsImage();
1146  ++m_uiPhaseSubphase;
1147  m_uiPhaseTimer = 8000;
1148  break;
1149  case 1:
1150  DoScriptText(SAY_COMMANDER_DAWNFORGE_3, m_creature);
1151  m_uiPhaseSubphase = 0;
1152  ++m_uiPhase;
1153  m_uiPhaseTimer = 8000;
1154  break;
1155  }
1156  break;
1157  case 7:

1160  case 0:

1162  ++m_uiPhaseSubphase;
1163  m_uiPhaseTimer = 12000;
1164  break;
1165  case 1:

1167  ++m_uiPhaseSubphase;
1168  m_uiPhaseTimer = 16000;

1174  m_uiPhaseTimer = 10000;

1405  m_uiSubEventTimer = 2000;
1406  m_uiSubEvent = 3;
1407  break;
1408  case 3: // Despawn machine after 2s

1410  pMachine->Use(m_creature);
1411 
1412  m_lastDraeneiMachineGuid.Clear();
1413  m_uiSubEventTimer = 0;
1414  m_uiSubEvent = 0;
1415  break;
1416  default:
1417  m_uiSubEventTimer = 0;
1418  break;
1419  }
1420  }
1421  else
1422  m_uiSubEventTimer -= uiDiff;
1423  }
1424  }
1425  else
1426  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1427  }

2876  return;
2877

2879  {

2884  if (!m_creature->IsAlive()) // should not be needed, IsAlive is checked in mangos before calling UpdateAI

2897  ResetPetCombat();
2898  return;
2899  }
2900

2903  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();

2906  {

2908 
2909  if (!owner)
2910  return;
2911

2913  {
2914  // Not correct in all cases.
2915  // When mob initiate attack by spell, pet should not start attack before spell landed.
2916  AttackStart(owner->getAttackerForHelper());
2917  }
2918  else if (m_creature->GetCharmInfo()->HasCommandState(COMMAND_FOLLOW))
2919  {

2921  if (!m_creature->hasUnitState(UNIT_STAT_FOLLOW))
2922  m_creature->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFollow(owner, PET_FOLLOW_DIST, PET_FOLLOW_ANGLE);
2923 
2924  // update when not in combat
2925  UpdateTimers(diff);
2926  }
2927  }

3738  m_crusaderStrikeTimer = 15000;
3739  return;
3740  }
3741  }
3742  else
3743  m_crusaderStrikeTimer -= diff;

3745  DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
